the aggregate purchase commitment of GM for offtake from both Phase 1 and from the Phase 2 Expansion under the
Amended Offtake Agreement will be equal to the lesser of (i) the lithium carbonate equivalent of 20% of GM’s requirements for lithium that is necessary for use in the production of battery cells manufactured by GM or its affiliates,
